matches up with what you have in mind.

00:14:41.690 --> 00:14:43.310
So? So? What kinda dream?

00:14:43.900 --> 00:14:48.690
I-I'm really self-conscious about it,
s-so please don't laugh.

00:14:48.940 --> 00:14:49.940
Yep, yep!

00:14:50.610 --> 00:14:52.240
I-In my dream,

00:14:52.780 --> 00:14:55.950
the manager told me he l-loved me.

00:14:56.320 --> 00:14:58.200
<i>Th-That's reality!</i>

00:14:56.700 --> 00:14:58.950
REALITY

00:14:59.450 --> 00:15:02.460
