did you answer him, Maika-chan?

00:15:02.660 --> 00:15:04.960
Y-Yes. I did.

00:15:05.830 --> 00:15:08.250
I said, "I love you, too."

00:15:09.840 --> 00:15:10.760
You, too, Kaho-san.

00:15:11.510 --> 00:15:15.470
And Mafuyu-san, Miu-san, 
Hideri-chan and Akizuki-san...

00:15:15.720 --> 00:15:18.260
I love all of you. 
That was my answer.

00:15:19.640 --> 00:15:20.770
Oh...

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:29.650
I feel sorry for him, but it sounds
like the manager doesn't have a chance.

00:15:29.650 --> 00:15:31.280
I'm not sure about that.

00:15:41.910 --> 00:15:45.420
Okay, try to snowboard today,
using what I taught you yesterday.

00:15:45.920 --> 00:15:46.960
Okay.

00:15:48.420 --> 00:15:49.790
Ma-Maika-san?

00:15:50.050 --> 00:15:50.750
Um...

00:15:50.960 --> 00:15:53.050
Wh-What?

00:15:53.470 --> 00:15:55.550
<i>Maika-san has a weird attitude!</i>

00:15:55.800 --> 00:15:58.510
<i>Did I make her practice too much
yesterday after all?</i>

00:15:58.970 --> 00:16:00.100
I'm sorry!

00:16:00.310 --> 00:16:03.100
Maika-san, you're just so kind
that I got carried away.

00:16:03.560 --> 00:16:06.140
I'm sorry for being so inconsiderate!

00:16:06.140 --> 00:16:07.730
Th-That's not true—

00:16:07.730 --> 00:16:09.860
Please don't hate me!

00:16:10.570 --> 00:16:11.860
It's okay, Manager—

00:16:11.860 --> 00:16:14.360
Please don't hate me!

00:16:15.070 --> 00:16:17.360
No! I don't want you to hate me!

00:16:17.740 --> 00:16:22.080
<i>I was so bothered by that dream
that it put me in a bad mood,</i>

00:16:22.330 --> 00:16:24.910
<i>which is making the manager sad!</i>

00:16:25.160 --> 00:16:27.250
<i>When he's going out of his way
to teach me...</i>

00:16:28.250 --> 00:16:29.130
<i>I have to</i>

00:16:29.330 --> 00:16:30.630
<i>clear up the misunderstanding!</i>

00:16:30.840 --> 00:16:32.710
Why? Why am I like this?

00:16:32.960 --> 00:16:34.840
It's okay, Manager!

00:16:37.550 --> 00:16:39.550
Manager...

00:16:40.430 --> 00:16:41.720
I love you!

00:16:42.890 --> 00:16:44.060
I'm sorry!

00:16:44.270 --> 00:16:45.810
Why are you apologizing?

00:16:46.350 --> 00:16:48.810
I'm sorry!

00:16:59.410 --> 00:17:02.580
Thank you for coming on Christmas,
two lonely guys!

00:17:02.910 --> 00:17:05.540
We really had a sadistic whip
cracked on us this year!

00:17:05.790 --> 00:17:07.620
Yeah, it's been awesome!

00:17:07.960 --> 00:17:10.380
Please don't come back here ever again.

00:17:12.250 --> 00:17:14.460
Good work, everyone!

00:17:14.840 --> 00:17:17.050
I'm calling it a year.

00:17:17.380 --> 00:17:21.510
Why don't we all finish the leftover cake?

00:17:22.010 --> 00:17:23.260
Yay!

00:17:25.100 --> 00:17:25.970
Owner!

00:17:26.220 --> 00:17:28.020
He brought you down?

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:29.900
Good for you!

00:17:32.560 --> 00:17:33.320
Hey!

00:17:33.570 --> 00:17:36.480
If you have enough time to be jealous
of a dog, help me instead.

00:17:37.820 --> 00:17:38.990
That's cute!

00:17:39.320 --> 00:17:40.990
He called it a "leftover,"

00:17:40.990 --> 00:17:43.370
but I bet he really made it for this!

00:17:43.620 --> 00:17:45.290
That's our manager!

00:17:45.540 --> 00:17:46.950
We see right through you!

00:17:48.080 --> 00:17:49.370
Here you go, Kaho-san.

00:17:51.500 --> 00:17:53.880
This time I did it
without being nervous at all!

00:17:57.300 --> 00:18:00.010
