At first it was just the manager,
Akizuki-kun and me.

00:18:13.190 --> 00:18:16.020
You two were the opening staff?

00:18:16.820 --> 00:18:18.900
I thought that would've included
the loli-granny...

00:18:21.990 --> 00:18:23.620
I came after them.

00:18:24.030 --> 00:18:24.950
Yeah.

00:18:25.370 --> 00:18:27.080
This brings back memories.

00:18:27.330 --> 00:18:29.700
Back when those two just started...

00:18:31.580 --> 00:18:34.130
<i>N-Nice to meet you.</i>

00:18:34.420 --> 00:18:36.250
