00:19:01.700 --> 00:19:02.780
Shut up!

00:19:02.780 --> 00:19:03.740
After all...

00:19:04.160 --> 00:19:06.740
I can't imagine that.

00:19:06.990 --> 00:19:09.490
I never change,
not even when I first meet someone.

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:13.250
